snippet.title: Mario's Little Odyssey
snippet.description:
In this video, I show off how to get all 19 stars in Mario's Little Odyssey a Super Mario 64 hack by Kaze, which are at these times:

Shifting Sand Kingdom  0:39
NSMB SM64 Kingdom  8:18
Lethal Lava Kingdom  10:21
Hazy Maze Kingdom  16:13
Rainbow Kingdom  18:26

Comments: This hack was kind of hard. Some of the jump didn't feel fair (I mean, this isn't NoD2 or anything like that), but aside from that, as well as some uninteresting environments, I thought this hack was alright.

Also, the music played in the castle will actually be heard after reselecting your file. I don't know why it does that.
